  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"\">\n   <div style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-left:8px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;padding-right:8px;margin-right:0px;\">\n    <blockquote style=\"padding:10px 10px 10px 20px;display:block;font-size:14px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);line-height:1.75;border-radius:0px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;overflow:auto;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);width:auto;margin-top:20px;border-width:3px;margin-bottom:20px;border-style:none none none solid;height:auto;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\"><span>微信支付正式发布「AI 专属卡」，WorkBuddy 率先接入。以后在 WorkBuddy 里，不只是可以让 AI 回答问题，还可以让它帮你找外卖、选套餐、领券、下单，甚至完成支付。</span></p>\n    </blockquote>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;visibility:visible;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">微信支付</span></span></span><span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;visibility:visible;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">正式发布</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(45, 123, 251);\"><span>「AI专属卡」</span></span><span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">，</span></span></span></span><span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;visibility:visible;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">WorkBuddy率先接入</span></span></span><span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;visibility:visible;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">——</span></span></span><span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;visibility:visible;text-decoration-style:initial;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">团购优惠，下单支付等，喊Ta帮你直接买！</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 240px;height: 232px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aecb9939&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKVER9adz906HcZ2GRwC61csAU2u7L1jLY7xicGnu60TWmKS8gSwdJibHgHmAxIib6VQHGeBH0CQwtiaep29AwSeKRu8gjkAh8OyJeBBojOqOnKg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 10px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0em;word-break:break-word;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n    <h3 style=\"padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><span style=\"border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);font-weight:bold;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:20px;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span>使用步骤</span></span></h3>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><strong><span style=\"padding:0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius:0px;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;margin-top:0px;border-width:3px;margin-bottom:0px;border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span style=\"font-size:17px;\">1. 先升级 WorkBuddy PC 端</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>将 WorkBuddy PC 端升级到&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:0px;padding:0px;font-weight:bold;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;margin-top:0px;border-width:3px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);margin-bottom:0px;border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span>5.1.1 及以上版本</span></strong><span>。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><strong><span style=\"padding:0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius:0px;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;margin-top:0px;border-width:3px;margin-bottom:0px;border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span style=\"font-size:17px;\">2. 打开「美团生活助手」</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>打开 WorkBuddy，进入「<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">专家</span>」页面，搜索并找到「<span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">美团生活助手</span>」。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>找到后，点击</span><span>「</span><span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">召唤</span></span><span>」</span><span>。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1d2ccddf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKVER9adz904jeRoaLutn4F4jL7aE3lbDB8EA2saE4QO9rjkCtrnxgskaqyRwqRZcuL7M2Nx6EJchY1hiajqAE0TkBXvwWowDLQIHGv1owrwg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><strong><span style=\"padding:0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius:0px;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;margin-top:0px;border-width:3px;margin-bottom:0px;border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span style=\"font-size:17px;\">3. 像和 AI 对话一样提出需求</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>召唤成功后，就可以像和普通 AI 对话一样，直接告诉 AI 你想买什么。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>比如：</span></p>\n    <blockquote style=\"padding:10px 10px 10px 20px;display:block;font-size:14px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);line-height:1.75;border-radius:0px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;overflow:auto;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);width:auto;margin-top:20px;border-width:3px;margin-bottom:20px;border-style:none none none solid;height:auto;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\"><span>帮我找附近 30 元以内的单人午餐套餐。</span><span> \n       <br> \n      </span><span>帮我点一杯咖啡。</span><span> \n       <br> \n      </span><span>我想吃不辣的，预算 35 元以内。</span></p>\n    </blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1em;margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8f07bfd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKVER9adz905DEe2mcS6QeszlQ3SeOdoFh5O7tu1Cmoya63ewhGKEAhUpicBmFDENmBGXNUgmjrApbdiaWXKoaXmibzibhcJeWNUBSmWxKo6zpck%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><strong><span style=\"padding:0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);border-radius:0px;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;margin-top:0px;border-width:3px;margin-bottom:0px;border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span style=\"font-size:17px;\">4. AI 帮你筛选、领券、下单</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>AI 会根据你的需求，帮你筛选、领券、下单，并用「AI 专属卡」完成支付。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC NEW&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;width:100%;margin-bottom:0px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;user-select:auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3019b391&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2Fjv69W6rKPNmibiaWteaMhYEoBzVcQS1BpUxcMMfIb9rFmpiao5D8cNkFllI6kev5wA0fGOFOJTibeF2401T21OuFkErRjkeYnzCVichEyA96UDEw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 10px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0em;word-break:break-word;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n    <h3 style=\"padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><span style=\"border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);font-weight:bold;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:20px;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span>AI 专属卡到底是什么？</span></span></h3>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>当订单进入支付环节时，就会用到微信支付的 AI 专属卡。它不是让 AI 随便花你的钱，而是在你授权的范围内，帮助完成指定场景的支付。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 10px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0em;word-break:break-word;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n    <h3 style=\"padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><span style=\"border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);font-weight:bold;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:20px;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span>它安全吗？会乱掏钱包吗？</span></span></h3>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>别慌，不是直接掏钱包。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>微信支付 AI 专属卡不是通过获取你的账户密码等重要信息直接提款，而是在你设定好的范围内、你允许的情况下，帮你购买和消费。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:0px 10px;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;overflow-wrap:break-word;word-spacing:0em;word-break:break-word;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;margin-top:0px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n    <h3 style=\"padding: 0px;display: block;text-align: left;margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><span style=\"border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);font-weight:bold;padding-left:10px;letter-spacing:0em;display:block;font-size:20px;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;line-height:1.5em;text-align:left;\"><span>彩蛋</span></span></h3>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>现在绑定，在 WorkBuddy 输入：</span></p>\n    <blockquote style=\"padding:10px 10px 10px 20px;display:block;font-size:14px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);line-height:1.75;border-radius:0px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px;overflow:auto;background:none left top / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);width:auto;margin-top:20px;border-width:3px;margin-bottom:20px;border-style:none none none solid;height:auto;\">\n     <p style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\"><span>帮我领美团优惠券</span></p>\n    </blockquote>\n    <p style=\"padding:8px 0px;margin:0px;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;text-align:left;\"><span>还有彩蛋惊喜嗷！欢迎评论区分享\"你的 AI 专属卡\"！</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-left:0px;padding-left:8px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;padding-right:8px;margin-right:0px;\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "微信支付发布「AI 专属卡」，WorkBuddy 率先接入，用户可通过自然语言对话让 AI 完成外卖搜索、领券、下单与支付全流程。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "微信支付发布「AI 专属卡」，WorkBuddy 率先接入，用户可通过自然语言对话让 AI 完成外卖搜索、领券、下单与支付全流程。",
  "summary": "本文是微信支付「AI 专属卡」的产品发布与使用指南。文章以 WorkBuddy 接入为例，介绍了用户通过自然语言对话让 AI 完成外卖搜索、套餐选择、优惠券领取、下单与支付的全流程操作步骤，并解释了 AI 专属卡的安全机制——在用户授权范围内完成指定场景支付，不直接获取账户密码。文章包含操作截图与视频演示，属于产品功能宣发类内容。",
